    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "First report of rare pomfrets (Teleostei: Bramidae) from Brazilian waters, with a key to Western Atlantic species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.191362>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.191364>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.191370> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.191362>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Eumegistus brevorti, freshly preserved male, 523 mm SL and 2.8 k, caught at 600 m depth 10 miles off Praia do Forte, Bahia, Northeast Brazil." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/191362/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.191364>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4 - A. The smallest Eumegistus brevorti specimen, TAMAR 0 0 35 (394 mm SL), showing white-tipped dorsal and anal fins lobes and caudal fin with black central rays, caught at the Praia do Forte, off Bahia, Northeast Brazil." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/191364/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.191370>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Ovaries of Eumegistus brevorti caught off Bahia, Northeast Brazil: 1: 11.16.2007: A 57.37 g; B: 93.25 g and 2: 09.07.2007: A: 10.06 g; B: 75.82 g." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/191370/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

